BEGIN:VEVENT
SUMMARY:"Ingenious": In Conversation 
DTSTART;TZID=America/Toronto:20170329T173000
DTEND;TZID=America/Toronto:20170329T190000
UID:32600108803
DESCRIPTION:https://www.eventbrite.ca/e/ingenious-in-conversation-tickets-
 32600108803\n\nPlease join Signal / McClelland & Stewart and Les ditions L
 a Presse for an in-conversation event.\nIngenious: How Canadian Innovators
  Made the World Smarter\, Smaller\, Kinder\, Safer\, Healthier\,\nWealthie
 r and Happier by Governor General David Johnston and Tom Jenkins\n\nWEDNES
 DAY\, MARCH 29\, 2017\,5:30 PM\nMaRS Discovery District\n101 College Stree
 t\, Toronto\nLower level auditorium\nOn stage conversation with Marci Ien\
 , Broadcast Journalist\, Bell Media\nFollowed by a book-signing\n\n\nSeati
 ng is limited.Please book tickets via Eventbrite.\n\n---------------------
 -----------\nJoignez-vous  Signal / McClelland & Stewart et aux ditions La
  Presse pour une conversation sur scne.\n\nIngnieux: Innovations canadienn
 es qui ont rendu le monde meilleur\ndu Gouverneur General David Johnston e
 t Tom Jenkins\n\nLE MERCREDI 29 MARS 2017\,17 h 30\nMaRS Discovery Distric
 t\n101\, rue College\, Toronto\nAuditorium de l'tage infrieur\nConversatio
 n sur scne avec Marci Ien\, journaliste dantenne\, Bell Media\nSuivie dune
